    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage, safe from the elements. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. It\u2019s a total dream to drive! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without that brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
