    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a superlative 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive example of the 996.2 generation's performance engineering. This wide-body specimen is powered by a mid-mounted 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus and an integrated dry-sump lubrication system. The power is delivered through a precise G96/31 6-speed manual transaxle and an advanced viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable; it has undergone a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a recent RMS replacement to ensure long-term reliability. The suspension geometry is preserved with factory-spec components, complemented by Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires mounted on pristine 18-inch Turbo-look wheels. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster with zero evidence of track-induced thermal stress or chassis fatigue. Inside, the cockpit features full-leather upholstery with no bolster wear, and all switchgear maintains original tactile feedback. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands mechanical transparency and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
